snippet.title: PKA Highlights
snippet.description:
This is The Highlight Clip Channel for the Painkiller already podcast(PKA)

PKA Business email = business@pkaonline.com




Description
PKA Clips and Highlights from the Painkiller Already Podcast

Hosts:              • Woody (WoodysGamertag)
                          • Kyle (FPSRussia) 
                          • Taylor (TaylorMurka)

Producer:         • DrChiz

__________________________________________

           Painkiller Already is a podcast that is hosted by WoodysGamertag, Kyle also known as FPSRussia and Taylor also known as TaylorMurka. The podcast has been steam-rolling through the airwaves & YouTube since early 2010. PKA discusses current events, news, relives comedic stories and gives their perspective on life while throwing in their comedic twist to all discussions
Bigups liquid richard, Bigups Sean ranklin Bigups gulagkingpin Bigups lummox
